title: Joe Rogan Experience Review of Yves Edwards
description:
JRE Review of MMA 69 with Yves Edwards

Yves a legend in the fight game and a great commentator. He is always so knowledgeable and nice to listen to on Rogan. I'm glad he was back to give some fight breakdowns and news. Enjoyed listening and reviewing!

Enjoy my review folks!
